      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The still from the feature film ‘Datorie şi sacrificiu’ (Duty and sacrifice) shows a group of men in traditional costume. There are three men in the centre of the picture. The first man on the right seems to be preparing to hit the man in the centre.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The feature was directed by Ion Sahighian and released in 1926.</ab>
